      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Northern Pacific has added\na new train, the Spokane limited,\nrunning from here to Seattle and\nTacoma The service begins SUM-\nday and it will cut an hour and As\nminutes from the time to the coast.\nThe train will carry sleepers, diner\nand observation cars. Leaving\nSpokane at p. m. and arriving on\nthe coast at 8 a. m. it will permit\ntransaction of business in Seattle\nor Tacoma and return that night.\nthe leaving time on the coast being\nthe same. The train eastbound\nreaches here at 9 a. m."
    }
